ABSTRACT
Disclosed is a location information determining method and
system for providing a variety of services based on a
location. The location information determining method
includes receiving cell information; and determining loca-
tion information that matches the cell information as loca-
tion information of a mobile terminal from a location
information database that stores location information that
matches a plurality of pieces of cell information, respec-
tively.
